China attaches great importance to the development of friendly
cooperation between the Chinese and Nigerian armed forces.
</P>
<P>
During talks with Abdul-Salam Abubakar, Nigerian chief of
defense staff, Fu said China treasures the friendship between the
Chinese and Nigerian people and armed forces.
</P>
<P>
