Chen Jian, director of the provincial bureau of posts and
telecommunications management, said that Qinghai has increased
investment in telecommunications since 1994 to cater to its
ever-booming economic development.
</P>
<P>
The provincial economy gained momentum in recent years after
the central government offered a more favorable tax and other
preferential policies, hoping to attract investment to the
landlocked areas from the rest of the country and overseas
businesses. 
