<HEADLINE> Problem of Vendors Getting Out of Control in </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LUSAKA, July 28 (Xinhua) -- Lusaka Province Minister Sonny
Mulenga has charged that the problem of vendors in Lusaka is
getting out of control and threatened to crack down on them,
Zambia Daily Mail reported today.
</P>
<P>
