<HEADLINE> Record High Tourism Earnings Expected in Slovakia </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PRAGUE, July 27 (Xinhua) -- Earnings by the tourism industry of
Slovakia are expected to reach a record high equivalent to 1.4
billion U.S. dollars this year, said the Slovak Tourism Bureau.
</P>
<P>
In the first half of the year, the country witnessed 9 percent
more tourist arrivals than the same period of last year, according
to the government bureau's latest statistics available today.
</P>
<P>
