to a total of 400,000, in the number of visits by foreign tourists
to this tiny Central European nation of 49,000 square kilometers.
</P>
<P>
The Slovak government in recent years has been taking measures
to protect the country's rich tourism resources, and improve and
expand facilities and services accommodating foreign visitors.
